  <brief_title>Pain Screening in Refugee Survivors of Torture</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Implementation of a Novel Pain-screening Tool in the Diagnoses of Pain Symptoms and Syndromes in Refugee Survivors of Torture</official_title>
  <sponsors>
